      <div class="postbody"> 
       <h3><a href="#p1001">Re: 【教程】如何使用Global Mapper 转换纸质地图或图片为标准地图</a></h3> 
       <p class="author"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=1001&amp;sid=fc0bb6b519ea1fb10bff6fff9b531487#p1001"><img src="./styles/prosilver/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="11" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a>by <strong><a href="./memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=495&amp;sid=fc0bb6b519ea1fb10bff6fff9b531487">jiulin</a></strong> &raquo; 2014-08-15 8:25 </p> 
